\b WHO:\b0\line "Type of vaccine: Live, attenuated\par
\par
Number of doses: One dose of 0.5 ml\par
\par
Boosters: A single dose of YF vaccine is sufficient to confer sustained lifelong protective immunity against YF disease; a booster dose is not necessary for protection but may still be required by some countries. Adjustments of the provisions for the duration of validity of certificates under the IHR are ongoing.\par
\par
